flowchart TB
    Exchanges([Exchanges /<br/>Market Data Vendors])
    Gateway[Market Data Gateway<br/>normalise + dedupe]
    Ticks[(Tick Stream<br/>keyed by instrument_id)]
    Evaluator[Rule Evaluator<br/>local subs + last_price]
    SubsDB[(Subscriptions Store<br/>source of truth)]
    Fired[(Fired Alerts Stream)]
    Dispatcher[Alert Dispatcher<br/>prefs + idempotency]
    Notif[Notification System<br/>push / email / SMS]
    Audit[(Audit Log<br/>object store)]

    Exchanges -->|feeds| Gateway
    Gateway --> Ticks
    Ticks --> Evaluator
    SubsDB -.->|CDC stream| Evaluator
    Evaluator --> Fired
    Fired --> Dispatcher
    Dispatcher --> Notif
    Fired -.-> Audit

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Exchanges external
    class Gateway,Evaluator,Dispatcher,Notif service
    class Ticks,SubsDB,Fired,Audit store
